title: Past Lives - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/10/22

description:
George Noory and Dr. Shelley Kaehr explore her research into past life regressions, where people examine visions and memories of past lives, and how discovering where your soul existed in the past can give insight into problems in the present day.
